h2. Installation

h3. Requirements

ThingFish is written in ruby, and is tested using version 1.8.6:

* Ruby (>= 1.8.6): "http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/downloads/":http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/downloads/

Other versions may work, but are not tested.

